# LeadRat Cline Rules

Read these files before any implementation:

{{LOAD_ORDER}}

AGENTS.md is the highest-priority source of truth.

Never create duplicate services, APIs, helpers, constants, models, enums, components, directives, or pipes.
Never use inline CSS.
Always search existing project patterns first.
Reuse shared components, existing CSS utilities, existing modal/confirmation patterns, and `getModuleListByAdvFilter()` where applicable.
Follow the existing Angular and NgRx architecture.
Keep changes minimal and protect existing user work.
